h-new-name-new-look\">\"Revamped Bowery Poetry to Open in March With New Name, New Look\"</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20140228232918/http://www.dnainfo.com/new-york/20130130/east-village/revamped-bowery-poetry-open-march-with-new-name-new-look\">Archived</a> 2014-02-28 at the <a href=\"/wiki/Wayback_Machine\" title=\"Wayback Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>. <i>DNAinfo</i> (January 30,20130</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Bowery_Poetry_Club&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.bowerypoetry.com\">Bowery Poetry Club website</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.boweryartsandscience.org/\">Bowery Arts and Science website</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.indiefeedpp.libsyn.com/index.php?search_string=UrbanaSlam&amp;Submit=Search&amp;search=1\">Poems Recorded Live at the Bowery Poetry Club (podcast series)</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://writing.upenn.edu/pennsound/x/Segue-BPC.html\">Archives of Segue Series</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.litkicks.com/August10BoweryPoetryClubNYC/\">Litkicks article on Brooklyn Poetry Day at the Bowery Poetry Club</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.allaboutjazz.com/php/news.php?id=17398\">All About Jazz on a Jazz event at the Bowery Poetry Club</a><sup class=\"noprint Inline-Template\"><span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">&#91;<i><a href=\"/wiki/Wikipedia:Link_rot\" title=\"Wikipedia:Link rot\"><span title=\"&#160;Dead link since Nove